snippet.title: Insights In Working With The Government Ft Amber Hanlon
snippet.description:
Before you connect with a small business, arm yourself with the specific information about the capabilities you can offer to large businesses. You shouldn't only think about winning contracts but also fulfilling and satisfying your customers by delivering what you promised.

With Amber Hanlon, Small Business Liaison Officer, small businesses can learn how to better improve in working to reach out to large business companies for subcontracting. Start today!

Watch Full Episode here : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UALAN1Ey0zQ&list=PL6-jBNNcc98vTBvNhFYfUTeH0k-Vx2VBH&index=28
